<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>장바구니 | DAMORE</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    :root {
      --bg: #f5f3ef;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --black: #111111;
      --muted: #6f6a63;
      --line: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.08);
      --gold: #9d8660;
      --shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      --radius: 24px;
      --max: 1280px;
      --red: #b23a2c;
      --red-bg: #fff1ee;
      --soft: #efe9df;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Pretendard", "Noto Sans KR", Arial, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--black);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
    }

    button {
      font: inherit;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: var(--max);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }

    .page {
      padding: 44px 0 80px;
    }

    .page-head {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .page-head small {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .page-head h1 {
      font-size: 42px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .page-head p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .top-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .top-btn {
      min-width: 160px;
      height: 48px;
      padding: 0 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      border: 0;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .top-btn-dark {
      background: #111;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .top-btn-light {
      background: var(--soft);
      color: #111;
    }

    .guide-box {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: #faf8f4;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .wrap {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .empty-box {
      padding: 48px 24px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
      background: #fcfaf7;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 20px;
    }

    .cart-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .cart-item {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: #fcfaf7;
      padding: 16px;
    }

    .cart-top {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .cart-thumb {
      width: 96px;
      height: 112px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      object-fit: cover;
      background: #efe9df;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .cart-info {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .cart-name {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.45;
      word-break: keep-all;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .cart-meta {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .cart-meta.bad {
      color: var(--red);
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .add-on-box {
      margin-top: 10px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: #faf8f4;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .add-on-box strong {
      color: var(--black);
    }

    .cart-bottom {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .qty-wrap {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .qty-box {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .qty-btn {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border: 0;
      background: #fff;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .qty-num {
      min-width: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .line-price {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 900;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .line-sub {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .remove-btn {
      height: 40px;
      padding: 0 16px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #efe9df;
      color: #111;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .summary-box {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .summary-row,
    .summary-total {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .summary-row {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .summary-total {
      margin-top: 8px;
      padding-top: 16px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .shipping-note {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: #faf8f4;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .checkout-btn {
      width: 100%;
      height: 58px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #111;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 18px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .checkout-btn.disabled {
      background: #d8d2c8;
      color: #7d756a;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .wrap {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .container {
        padding: 0 16px;
      }

      .card {
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .page-head h1 {
        font-size: 34px;
      }

      .top-btn {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .cart-top {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .cart-thumb {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        aspect-ratio: 1 / 1.08;
      }

      .cart-bottom {
        align-items: stretch;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%
    const safeCart = Array.isArray(cart) ? cart : [];

    const FREE_SHIPPING_MIN = 70000;
    const BASIC_SHIPPING_FEE = 3000;

    const hasStockIssue = safeCart.some((item) => {
      const stock = Number(item.stock || 0);
      const qty = Number(item.quantity || 0);
      return stock <= 0 || qty > stock || item.productStatus === 'soldout';
    });

    const productOnlyTotal = safeCart.reduce((sum, item) => {
      return sum + (Number(item.price || 0) * Number(item.quantity || 0));
    }, 0);

    const addOnGrandTotal = safeCart.reduce((sum, item) => {
      return sum + Number(item.addOnTotal || 0);
    }, 0);

    const subtotal = productOnlyTotal + addOnGrandTotal;
    const shippingFee = subtotal >= FREE_SHIPPING_MIN || subtotal === 0 ? 0 : BASIC_SHIPPING_FEE;
    const finalTotal = subtotal + shippingFee;
  %>

  <main class="page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-head">
        <small>Cart</small>
        <h1>장바구니</h1>
        <p>선택한 상품을 확인하고 주문 단계로 넘어갈 수 있습니다.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="top-actions">
        <a href="/" class="top-btn top-btn-dark">쇼핑 계속하기</a>
        <button type="button" class="top-btn top-btn-light" onclick="history.back()">뒤로가기</button>
      </div>

      <div class="guide-box">
        주문 금액 <strong><%= FREE_SHIPPING_MIN.toLocaleString() %>원</strong> 이상이면 무료배송,
        미만이면 배송비 <strong><%= BASIC_SHIPPING_FEE.toLocaleString() %>원</strong>이 추가됩니다.
      </div>

      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="card">
          <h2 class="section-title">담은 상품</h2>

          <% if (safeCart.length === 0) { %>
            <div class="empty-box">
              장바구니에 담긴 상품이 없습니다.
            </div>
          <% } else { %>
            <div class="cart-list">
              <% safeCart.forEach((item) => { %>
                <%
                  const addOnNames = Array.isArray(item.addOnNames) ? item.addOnNames : [];
                  const addOnTotal = Number(item.addOnTotal || 0);
                  const lineProductTotal = Number(item.price || 0) * Number(item.quantity || 0);
                  const lineTotal = lineProductTotal + addOnTotal;
                  const hasIssue =
                    Number(item.stock || 0) <= 0 ||
                    Number(item.quantity || 0) > Number(item.stock || 0) ||
                    item.productStatus === 'soldout';
                %>

                <div class="cart-item">
                  <div class="cart-top">
                    <% if (item.image) { %>
                      <img src="<%= item.image %>" alt="<%= item.name %>" class="cart-thumb">
                    <% } else { %>
                      <div class="cart-thumb"></div>
                    <% } %>

                    <div class="cart-info">
                      <div class="cart-name"><%= item.name %></div>

                      <% if (item.option) { %>
                        <div class="cart-meta">옵션: <%= item.option %></div>
                      <% } %>

                      <% if (item.color) { %>
                        <div class="cart-meta">컬러: <%= item.color %></div>
                      <% } %>

                      <div class="cart-meta">상품금액: <%= Number(item.price || 0).toLocaleString() %>원</div>

                      <% if (typeof item.stock !== 'undefined') { %>
                        <div class="cart-meta <%= hasIssue ? 'bad' : '' %>">
                          재고: <%= Number(item.stock || 0) %>개
                          <% if (hasIssue) { %> / 주문 불가<% } %>
                        </div>
                      <% } %>

                      <% if (addOnNames.length > 0) { %>
                        <div class="add-on-box">
                          <strong>추가상품</strong><br>
                          <%= addOnNames.join(', ') %>
                          <% if (addOnTotal > 0) { %>
                            <br>추가금액: <strong><%= addOnTotal.toLocaleString() %>원</strong>
                          <% } %>
                        </div>
                      <% } %>

                      <div class="cart-bottom">
                        <div class="qty-wrap">
                          <form method="POST" action="/cart/decrease" style="display:inline;">
                            <input type="hidden" name="productId" value="<%= item.productId %>">
                            <input type="hidden" name="selectedOption" value="<%= item.option || '' %>">
                            <input type="hidden" name="selectedColor" value="<%= item.color || '' %>">
                            <input type="hidden" name="selectedAddOnIds" value="<%= Array.isArray(item.addOnIds) ? item.addOnIds.join(',') : '' %>">
                            <button type="submit" class="qty-btn">-</button>
                          </form>

                          <div class="qty-box">
                            <div class="qty-num"><%= item.quantity %></div>
                          </div>

                          <form method="POST" action="/cart/increase" style="display:inline;">
                            <input type="hidden" name="productId" value="<%= item.productId %>">
                            <input type="hidden" name="selectedOption" value="<%= item.option || '' %>">
                            <input type="hidden" name="selectedColor" value="<%= item.color || '' %>">
                            <input type="hidden" name="selectedAddOnIds" value="<%= Array.isArray(item.addOnIds) ? item.addOnIds.join(',') : '' %>">
                            <button type="submit" class="qty-btn">+</button>
                          </form>

                          <form method="POST" action="/cart/remove" style="display:inline;">
                            <input type="hidden" name="productId" value="<%= item.productId %>">
                            <input type="hidden" name="selectedOption" value="<%= item.option || '' %>">
                            <input type="hidden" name="selectedColor" value="<%= item.color || '' %>">
                            <input type="hidden" name="selectedAddOnIds" value="<%= Array.isArray(item.addOnIds) ? item.addOnIds.join(',') : '' %>">
                            <button type="submit" class="remove-btn">삭제</button>
                          </form>
                        </div>

                        <div class="line-price">
                          <%= lineTotal.toLocaleString() %>원
                          <div class="line-sub">
                            <%= Number(item.price || 0).toLocaleString() %>원 × <%= item.quantity %>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              <% }) %>
            </div>
          <% } %>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h2 class="section-title">결제 예정 금액</h2>

          <div class="summary-box">
            <div class="summary-row">
              <span>상품 합계</span>
              <strong><%= productOnlyTotal.toLocaleString() %>원</strong>
            </div>

            <div class="summary-row">
              <span>추가상품 합계</span>
              <strong><%= addOnGrandTotal.toLocaleString() %>원</strong>
            </div>

            <div class="summary-row">
              <span>배송비</span>
              <strong><%= shippingFee.toLocaleString() %>원</strong>
            </div>

            <div class="summary-total">
              <span>최종 금액</span>
              <span><%= finalTotal.toLocaleString() %>원</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="shipping-note">
            <% if (safeCart.length === 0) { %>
              상품을 담으면 결제 금액이 계산됩니다.
            <% } else if (shippingFee === 0) { %>
              무료배송 적용됨
            <% } else { %>
              <%= FREE_SHIPPING_MIN.toLocaleString() %>원 이상 구매 시 무료배송
            <% } %>
          </div>

          <% if (safeCart.length === 0 || hasStockIssue) { %>
            <a href="/order" class="checkout-btn disabled">
              <% if (safeCart.length === 0) { %>
                담긴 상품이 없습니다
              <% } else { %>
                재고 문제 해결 후 주문 가능
              <% } %>
            </a>
          <% } else { %>
            <a href="/order" class="checkout-btn">주문하기</a>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>